Class ValUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jessemull.microflexinteger.util.ValUtil

  • public class ValUtil
extends Object
    This class validates well, well sets, plates and stacks by checking for null values and wells outside a range of indices.
    Author:
    Jesse L. Mull
